":"12197","username":"茶卡特尔","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"11905","dbdateline":"1557040885","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"43569498","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2019-5-5 15:34","message":"伞哥哥不过是个高中生，青春是允许犯错啊，伞哥哥最后也没有放弃长笛，也没有放弃自己的原则。<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />我是相信伞哥哥经历种种后会成熟起来最后找到自己的道路走向幸福的人生，而且伞哥哥也不是孤身一人，大家这不是都爱伞哥哥嘛<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"12198","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"11906","dbdateline":"1557041651","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"43571208","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2019-5-5 17:29","message":"S1没开摸鱼的时候看了看管乐版的图兰朵，龙圣的版本大概是和2006年崎玉荣高一样是后藤洋编曲版吧，<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />有意思的是最后奏和黄主席谈话的时候，龙圣的演奏临近结束，最后那段曲子的名字是《おお神聖なる父君陛下よ》（Padre augusto）（虽然那段唱词是歌颂爱），大家体会一下<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n久石奏“那时候，我仿佛见证了北宇治帝王的诞生”<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"12199","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"11907","dbdateline":"1557048585","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"43571260","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-5-5 17:34","message":"所以可以盖棺了么，武田写のぞみぞ非常到位，但是对阿伞本人塑造不太行，山田反之。这么看也不错，各取所需，感觉凑一块是个完美的组合<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/037.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"12200","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"11908","dbdateline":"1557048861","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"43571812","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author"